                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable.</hi>) I produce a certificate of Wat<lb></lb>son's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted</hi> 15<hi rend="italic">th April, of larceny from the person; confined six months and whipped</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
